{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1801630, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 353971, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我一直觉得自己是父母生命的延续，我不仅在伦理上，更在遗传意义上我父母的延续，某种程度上有种“我即我父母”的感觉，所以我也非常希望自己有这样一个生命的延续，这让我不再过于害怕死亡", "timestamp": 1623025275, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1801631, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 353971, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "也算是种人生体验", "timestamp": 1623025307, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1801639, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 353971, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我喜欢且需要那种无条件爱一个人的感觉", "timestamp": 1623025564, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1801640, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 353971, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "能和喜欢的人有一个小孩子会很幸福qwq", "timestamp": 1623025591, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1801654, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 353971, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "补充一下问题，衡量一下经济投入/时间精力投入/母亲事业发展受阻等等因素，会不会觉得养孩子是一桩亏本生意？为什么在明知道养孩子很辛苦的情况下，依然有很多人选择生养小孩呢？（dz觉得这些人很勇敢，但是也有点不解）", "timestamp": 1623025892, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1801689, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 353971, "reply_to": 1801654, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 解锁人生成就，理解什么是最接近无私的举动", "timestamp": 1623027066, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1801691, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 353971, "reply_to": 1801654, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 繁衍是人类的更原始本能。经济投入等只是当前的社会结构带给我们需要考虑的事情。", "timestamp": 1623027129, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1801695, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 353971, "reply_to": 1801654, "tag": null, "text": "社会组织阻碍人类本能，况且这个本能不属于违反道德的那种，说明社会组织形式出了问题，而非生孩子出了问题", "timestamp": 1623027200, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1801704, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 353971, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "人这么喜欢被金钱社会异化啊", "timestamp": 1623027525, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1801744, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 353971, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "解锁人生成就+1 还有就是想知道自己和男票能造出个什么样的小孩哈哈哈", "timestamp": 1623028915, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1801750, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 353971, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我觉得养孩子从来都不应该被当作一种生意来衡量利弊，从来没有“亏本”一说", "timestamp": 1623029044, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1801781, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 353971, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "#353490\nxs完美", "timestamp": 1623029617, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1801885, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 353971, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "没准就能成太上皇了呢", "timestamp": 1623031408, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1802680, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 353971, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不要爸妈会急", "timestamp": 1623039492, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1804196, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 353971, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "人类幼崽好可爱呀，好想自己生一个玩玩；不过真的养不起呀，所以虽然很想要但实际上可能也不会要吧", "timestamp": 1623056169, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 8, "pid": 353971, "reply": 15, "tag": null, "text": "想要小孩的人是出于什么想法和动机呢？纯好奇，欢迎讨论", "timestamp": 1623024726, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1623056170, "url": "", "vote": {}}}